<DOCNO> LA082194-0209 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 071877 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
August 21, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Page 86; Calendar Desk 
</P>
