<TEXT>
<P>
 A birthday party brawl that broke out early Saturday morning in the 200 block 
of Bard Lane just outside the Ventura city limits left two young men in 
critical condition and three others slightly injured, a Ventura County 
Sheriff's Department spokesman said. 
</P>
<P>
 The fight started about 1 a.m. after youths from the Ventura Avenue area 
crashed the party, the spokesman said.Police estimate that more than 50 youths 
at the scene participated in the fight using bricks, clubs and other weapons. 
</P>
