listed in critical condition with head injuries at Ventura County Medical 
Center, a hospital spokeswoman said. Juan Rodriguez, 19; Oscar Ponce, 23, and 
Ricardo Vasquez, 18, all of Oxnard, were treated for minor injuries and 
released, the spokeswoman said. 
