<P>
 A group of Ventura residents will host a community block party to raise funds 
for a playground at a midtown elementary school. 
</P>
<P>
 The residents are asking the community to donate items for a yard sale to be 
held during the fund-raiser, which is scheduled to take place at Blanche 
