<P>
NEWS, TIPS & BARGAINS: DAILY UPDATES ON WESTERN FIRES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Five Western states are pooling information to provide daily updates on the 
forest fires raging across that region. 
</P>
<P>
 Travelers calling (800) 704-3246 can obtain the latest news on the status of 
recreation areas, road closures and warnings in Idaho, Oregon, Washington, 
Montana and Wyoming. As of midweek press-time, the recording for Idaho -- site 
of the greatest number of fires -- was the longest, running nearly five 
minutes. Also in the recording, each state provides several telephone numbers 
to call for more information. 
</P>
