NEWS, TIPS & BARGAINS: NEW INFO-CENTRAL IN SONOMA VALLEY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A new Sonoma Valley Visitor Information Center will open Aug. 27 at the 
entrance to the Viansa Winery, 25200 Arnold Drive (Highway 121). The center, 
